				</blockquote>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Prestige Award Section -->
		<section class="award-section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="award-content">
					<h3 class="award-title">My Prestige Award</h3>
					<p class="award-text">
						Nitin's greatest strength is his ability to separate himself from the crowd that believes intensity goes hand in hand with volume, aggression and excessive effects. He brings a sense of balance and measure to the music that allows him to build tension by contrast, not bombast.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- About Me Section -->
		<section id="about" class="about-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h3 class="section-heading">About Me</h3>
				<div class="about-grid">
					<div class="about-text-content">
						<p>
							Welcome to the official website of <strong>Nitin Nigam</strong>, a passionate musician and guitarist dedicated to creating beautiful music and sharing the art of guitar with the world.
						</p>
						<p>
							With years of experience and a deep love for music, I strive to create melodies that touch hearts and inspire others to discover the beauty of musical expression. My journey in music has been one of constant learning, exploration, and dedication to the craft.
						</p>
						<p>
							Through my performances, compositions, and teaching, I aim to bridge the gap between technical mastery and emotional expression, creating music that resonates with audiences worldwide.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Live & Studio Section -->
		<section class="live-studio-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h3 class="section-heading">Live & Studio</h3>
				<div class="live-studio-grid">
					<div class="live-studio-text">
						<p>
							Whether performing live on stage or working in the studio, I bring the same passion and dedication to every project. My live performances are known for their energy and emotional depth, while my studio work focuses on capturing the perfect moment and creating timeless recordings.
						</p>
						<p>
							I've had the privilege of performing at various venues and festivals, sharing the stage with talented musicians and connecting with audiences through the universal language of music.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Professional Skills Section -->
		<section class="skills-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h3 class="section-heading">Professional Skills</h3>
				<div class="skills-grid">
					<div class="skill-card">
						<h4 class="skill-title">Music<br>Theory</h4>
					</div>
					<div class="skill-card">
						<h4 class="skill-title">Pentatonic<br>scales</h4>
					</div>
					<div class="skill-card">
						<h4 class="skill-title">Tuning By<br>ear</h4>
					</div>
					<div class="skill-card">
						<h4 class="skill-title">Strumming<br>patterns</h4>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Guitar Lessons Section -->
		<section id="lessons" class="lessons-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h3 class="section-heading">Guitar Lessons</h3>
				<div class="lessons-content">
					<p>
						I offer personalized guitar lessons for students of all levels, from beginners to advanced players. My teaching approach combines technical instruction with creative expression, helping students develop both their skills and their musical voice.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Tab, Techniques & Tips Section -->
		<section class="tips-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h3 class="section-heading">Tab, Techniques & Tips</h3>
				<div class="tips-content">
					<p>
						Explore my collection of guitar tabs, techniques, and tips designed to help you improve your playing. From basic chord progressions to advanced fingerpicking patterns, I share insights from years of experience to help you on your musical journey.
					</p>
					<p>
						Each lesson is crafted with care, focusing on practical application and musical understanding. Whether you're learning your first song or mastering complex solos, these resources are designed to support your growth as a guitarist.
					</p>
					<a href="#contact" class="enroll-btn">Enroll</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Next Tours Section -->
		<section id="shows" class="tours-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h3 class="section-heading">Next Tours</h3>
				<div class="tours-list">
